snippet: Rockets fired from Lebanon hit Israeli territory on Saturday and Israel's army responded with artillery fire, Lebanese security sources and the Israeli military said, in the second such incident in two days....

headline.print_headline: Israel Fires Into Lebanon After Rockets Launched Over Border
headline.main: Israel Fires Into Lebanon After Rockets Launched Over Border

lead_paragraph: Rockets fired from Lebanon hit Israeli territory on Saturday and Israel's army responded with artillery fire, Lebanese security sources and the Israeli military said, in the second such incident in two days.
